Getting the system ready for app development using Expo CLI

Need to install:
	- Nodejs: DONE - Version 18.16.0
	- Git: DONE - Version 2.25.1
		- Need to set up git username and email
	- Watchman: DONE - Version 4.9.0

Install Expo
	- npm add expo: DONE

To Run App:
	- cd into Desktop/App/Frontend/WarehouseFE
	- sudo npx expo start
	- scan QR code using camera - must have expo go app

To Run Flask:
    - cd into Desktop/App/Backend/WarehouseBE
    - export FLASK_APP=WarehouseBEAPI.py
    - WarehouseBEVenv/bin/activate
    - flask run --host=0.0.0.0
